== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2019年1月25日，[[Netflix|Netflix]]宣佈給予影集整季預訂，共6集<ref name="SeriesOrder">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/netflix-the-crown-producers-team-for-behind-her-eyes-1203117999/|title=‘The Crown’ Producers Making Psychological Thriller ‘Behind Her Eyes’ for Netflix|last=Clarke|first=Stewart|publisher=Variety|date=2019-01-25|accessdate=2019-02-07|archive-date=2019-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126015513/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/netflix-the-crown-producers-team-for-behind-her-eyes-1203117999/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|史提夫·萊福特|Steve Lightfoot}}擔當節目統籌兼執行監製<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-orders-limited-drama-series-behind-her-eyes|title=Netflix orders limited drama series Behind Her Eyes|website=Netflix Media Center|accessdate=2019-01-25|archive-date=2019-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209124305/https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-orders-limited-drama-series-behind-her-eyes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年8月，艾瑞克·里希特·斯特蘭德（{{lang|en|Erik Richter Strand}}）確定執導影集<ref name="Casting"/>。

=== 選角 ===
2019年8月，{{le|席夢娜·布朗|Simona Brown}}、{{le|依芙·霍森|Eve Hewson}}、[[湯姆·巴特曼|湯姆·巴特曼]]和{{le|羅柏·亞倫梅耶|Robert Aramayo}}確定領銜出演影集<ref name="Casting">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/netflix-behind-her-eyes-eve-hewson-simona-brown-the-crown-1203296630/|title=Netflix’s ‘Behind Her Eyes,’ From ‘The Crown’ Producers, Sets Cast|last=Clarke|first=Stewart|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2019-08-08|access-date=2019-08-08|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808100442/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/netflix-behind-her-eyes-eve-hewson-simona-brown-the-crown-1203296630/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/behind-her-eyes-simona-brown-tom-bateman-eve-hewson-1202664233/|title=‘Behind Her Eyes’: Simona Brown, Tom Bateman & Eve Hewson Star In Netflix Psychological Thriller|first2=Andreas|last2=Wiseman|first=Peter|last=White|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-08-08|access-date=2019-08-08|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808111659/https://deadline.com/2019/08/behind-her-eyes-simona-brown-tom-bateman-eve-hewson-1202664233/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2019年6月在[[倫敦|倫敦]]和[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]開機，10月殺青<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.backstage.com/uk/magazine/article/get-cast-in-new-netflix-thriller-series-behind-her-eyes-67828/|title=Get Cast in New Netflix Thriller Series ‘Behind Her Eyes’|last=Cook|first=Laurence|publisher=Backstage|date=2019-04-15|accessdate=2019-05-07|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422061202/https://www.backstage.com/uk/magazine/article/get-cast-in-new-netflix-thriller-series-behind-her-eyes-67828/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

